snippet.title: Beyonce Admits Illuminati Membership to Oprah Winfrey, Reports The Huffington Post?

localized.description:
Beyonce admits being a member of the Illuminati in Oprah Winfrey interview, according to a satire article published by The Huffington Post, but even though the article is satire, is it really that far from the truth?  Mark Dice breaks it down.

His viral videos have received more than 140 million views and have received international media attention.
